    "description": "・卡片战斗游戏+视觉小说游戏<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2286790/extras/ef1d1c03f435dc4876b0c38bc0fa0905.poster.avif?t=1678683638\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2286790/extras/ef1d1c03f435dc4876b0c38bc0fa0905.webm?t=1678683638\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2286790/extras/ef1d1c03f435dc4876b0c38bc0fa0905.mp4?t=1678683638\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>卡片战斗游戏和视觉小说游戏的结合。<br>战斗类似于传统的roguelike卡组游戏，但我们试图通过包括许多战略元素，如卡牌合成、技能和组合系统，使其充满活力。<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2286790/extras/0a795d73bb5181da3812ad78eddb57f6.poster.avif?t=1678683638\" width=600 height=310 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2286790/extras/0a795d73bb5181da3812ad78eddb57f6.webm?t=1678683638\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2286790/extras/0a795d73bb5181da3812ad78eddb57f6.mp4?t=1678683638\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>包括RPG元素。<br>获得经验，提高等级，并选择适合你的游戏风格的技能。<br>你还可以获得各种食物和收集文物来帮助你度过难关。<br><br><br><br>・故事模式<br><br>玩故事模式，享受各种事件和故事。<br>如果你想测试一下你的技能，可以试试roguelike模式!<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2286790/extras/19d55703f6ac02de05fe06b530a68a92.poster.avif?t=1678683638\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2286790/extras/19d55703f6ac02de05fe06b530a68a92.webm?t=1678683638\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2286790/extras/19d55703f6ac02de05fe06b530a68a92.mp4?t=1678683638\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>故事模式让你享受主角头盔人的独特故事。<br>在城市中巡逻，解决案件并帮助有困难的市民。<br>你会遇到异性成员，并经历不同的事件和事故。<br>但别忘了，你的最终目标是打败所有的恶魔派，从他们手中夺回老城。<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2286790/extras/80bceaa6ab31b5d1c92b2731a05104b6.poster.avif?t=1678683638\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2286790/extras/80bceaa6ab31b5d1c92b2731a05104b6.webm?t=1678683638\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2286790/extras/80bceaa6ab31b5d1c92b2731a05104b6.mp4?t=1678683638\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>扮演现实生活中的英雄--头盔人，享受与独特人物和各种事件的互动。<br><br><br>・罗格利克模式<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2286790/extras/26082bd75b742688d8ccaaf677ab2e98.poster.avif?t=1678683638\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2286790/extras/26082bd75b742688d8ccaaf677ab2e98.webm?t=1678683638\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2286790/extras/26082bd75b742688d8ccaaf677ab2e98.mp4?t=1678683638\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>无赖模式是一种具有挑战性的模式。<br>你将不得不在四个大的章节和56个随机放置的阶段中战斗。<br>如果你在战斗中死亡，你的卡组和角色将被重置，但不要气馁。<br>你可以使用你收集的点数使你的角色更强大<br><br><br><br>*将增加新的可玩人物。 <br>还计划进行多角色的多人对战，各种模式，以及挑战系统。<br>请继续关注更多的人物和不同的故事。",
